I/S Reformulation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The main issue with the income statement is that the tax expense belongs
 to both the operating part and the financial part.
 The issue is: how to take that expense and split it between these 2 parts?
 Some assumption has to be made: calculation of the 
\series bold
average tax percentage rate
\series default
 (take the income tax expense, divided by income before tax).
